<codeline lineno="88"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="89"><highlight class="comment"><sp/><sp/>All<sp/>the<sp/>TRUST<sp/>libraries<sp/>(LIBLATAFILTER<sp/>notably)<sp/>and<sp/>all<sp/>the<sp/>main<sp/>C++<sp/>source<sp/>code<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>compiled<sp/>in<sp/>either<sp/>32b<sp/>or<sp/>64b<sp/>depending</highlight></codeline>
