<codeline lineno="110"><highlight class="comment"><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="111"><highlight class="comment"><sp/><sp/>For<sp/>the<sp/>IJK<sp/>parts<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>code,<sp/>the<sp/>rule<sp/>is<sp/>that<sp/>:<sp/>the<sp/>three<sp/>directions<sp/>nx,<sp/>ny<sp/>and<sp/>nz<sp/>are<sp/>always<sp/>within<sp/>32b,<sp/>but<sp/>their<sp/>*product*<sp/>might<sp/>exceed<sp/>32b.</highlight></codeline>
